mergeData.warningText: Other users have {action} the process, and the data has changed ( {mainFormFieldCount} fields in {subformCount} tables). Please confirm the data before continuing
mergeData.tableMergeRule:
1. Non conflicting row data will not be displayed, including locally added row data;
2、 The row data with updated values or current values is identified as updated, and the updated values overwrite the current values;
3、 The newly added row data with the latest value is marked as new and will be added to the current value after the update;
4、 The row data deleted from the latest value is marked as deleted and will be deleted from the current value after updating;
5、 The row data deleted from the current value is identified as locally deleted and will be restored to the current value after updating.
